00:12:12.380 --> 00:12:19.060
them so so two step process so they want repped
writers you're not just meeting somebody at

00:12:19.060 --> 00:12:25.089
a coffee shop and hey what I want to bring
you in why don't you yeah I mean I think TV

00:12:25.089 --> 00:12:30.269
is a little bit yeah harder than features
to get in with with features you can get in

00:12:30.269 --> 00:12:33.959
I think a little bit easier meet producers
and talk TV 's a little bit tougher without

00:12:33.959 --> 00:12:39.350
an agency but it depends on what you're trying
to do if you're a screenwriter and you want

00:12:39.350 --> 00:12:43.959
to work in TV are you trying to sell a show
